CatDescriptText: Cutline of related article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 16, 1965, page 6, reads: "OES Chapter To Honor Past Matrons - Jerusalem Chapter 75 Order of Eastern Star, will sponsor a banquet on Sunday, Oct. 24, honoring the chapter's past matrons. To take place Sunday, Oct. 24, at 6 P.M., the banquet will be held at the Top of the Towers Restaurant in the Gateway Towers."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of the Jerusalem Chapter of Eastern Star members, including Wilhelmina Byrd Brown, seated fifth on left, gathered behind banquet table, in Top of the Towers Restaurant, another version
